OL,3,CSecond child dies following a crash on
OL,4,Cthe A30 in Cornwall
OL,6,FA second child has died following a
OL,7,Froad crash on the A30 in Cornwall.
OL,9,FEmergency services were called shortly
OL,10,Fbefore 11am on Friday 29 May following
OL,11,Fa crash involving multiple vehicles in
OL,12,Fthe westbound carriageway of the A30
OL,13,Fnear Connor Downs.
OL,15,FAn eight-year-old boy died at the
OL,16,Fscene, while a five-year-old boy was
OL,17,Ftaken to Bristol Children's Hospital
OL,18,Fwith serious injuries but died on
OL,19,FTuesday 2 June.
