OL,3,CSecond child dies following a crash on
OL,4,Cthe A30 in Cornwall
OL,6,FA woman in her 70s is being treated in
OL,7,FDerriford Hospital having suffered
OL,8,Fserious injuries. A woman in her 40s
OL,9,Fwas treated for injuries at Derriford
OL,10,Fhospital and has since been discharged.
OL,12,FThe two women and two children were
OL,13,Ftravelling in the same car.
OL,15,FRelatives are being supported by
OL,16,Fspecially trained officers.
