OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780665075
OL,3,CSecond child dies following a crash on
OL,4,Cthe A30 in Cornwall
OL,6,FA local man in his 60s was arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of causing death by
OL,8,Fdangerous driving and causing serious
OL,9,Finjury by dangerous driving. He was
OL,10,Ftreated for minor injuries.
OL,12,FHe has been released under
OL,13,Finvestigation while the investigation
OL,14,Fcontinues.
OL,16,FDetective Inspector Andy Heath of
OL,17,FDevon and Cornwall Police Serious
OL,18,FCollisions Investigation Team said: "I
OL,19,Fam saddened to confirm that a second
OL,20,Fboy has passed away following Friday's
OL,21,Fcollision on the A30.
OL,26,@zD@eOU
