OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780665075
OL,3,CSecond child dies following a crash on
OL,4,Cthe A30 in Cornwall
OL,6,F"It is important that the family are
OL,7,Fgiven the privacy needed at this
OL,8,Fdifficult time and my thoughts remain
OL,9,Fwith them and others affected by this
OL,10,Ftragic incident. Investigators
OL,11,Fcontinue to support the relatives
OL,12,Fwhile we secure the evidence required
OL,13,Fin this case.
OL,15,F"I would like to thank those who have
OL,16,Fresponded to our witness appeals this
OL,17,Fweek and ask that any witness who has
OL,18,Fnot yet contacted us or anyone with
OL,19,Frelevant dash-cam to please call 101
OL,20,For make contact via our website
OL,21,Fquoting 50260136471."
